The *~ListSubpages* [[Help:WikiPlugin|plugin]] lists the names of all sub-pages of a given page (by default the current page).

== Usage

<verbatim>
<?plugin ListSubpages ?>
</verbatim>

== Arguments

{| class="bordered"
|-
! Argument
! Description
! Default value
|-
| <b>basepage</b>
| The page to execute upon
| Current pagename
|-
| <b>maxpages</b>
| Maximum number of pages to include
| none
|}

== Example

<verbatim>
<?plugin ListSubpages basepage=Help maxpages=10 ?>
</verbatim>

<?plugin ListSubpages basepage=Help maxpages=10 ?>

